Package: pinfo201
Type: Package
Title: Practice Sets for Foundation Skills for Data Science
Version: 0.1.0
Author: David Hendry
Maintainer: David Hendry <dhendry@uw.edu>
Description: This package enables instructors to create practice sets for learning to code in R. In addition to giving learners basic coding tasks and feedback, this package provides functions for automatically grading student work.
    This package installs an Addin menu into RStudio, which learner use to select practice sets and have their work checked. Instructions are given a set of admin functions for creating practice sets and grading student work.
    Instruction sets are specified with a small number of markup tags, which are used to wrap R code.
